most powerful,

68
00:05:38,779 --> 00:05:41,447
most ambitious planetary
defense system

69
00:05:41,615 --> 00:05:42,907
ever conceived.

70
00:05:43,075 --> 00:05:45,660
lt's equipped
with an energy field

71
