distress call.

221
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:11,885
Can anybody read?

222
00:15:12,053 --> 00:15:14,054
No way.

223
00:15:15,473 --> 00:15:18,308
What?

224
00:15:18,476 --> 00:15:22,395
This is Victoria Preston
on the USS Nautilus. Come in.

225
00:15:25,524 --> 00:15:28,151
lsn't the Nautilus the spacecraft
that's on the Mercury mission?

226
00:15:28,319 --> 00:15:30,862
