into Mercury.

590
00:42:52,521 --> 00:42:54,939
Oh, my God,
the magnetism.

591
00:42:56,399 --> 00:43:00,277
Vic, there's been
a huge magnetic event.

592
00:43:00,445 --> 00:43:03,447
Yes, l know.
We were right in the middle of it.

593
00:43:03,615 --> 00:43:07,618
Mercury's been magnetized
and is being pushed out of its orbit.

594
00:43:09,120 --> 00:43:11,997
Magnetism.
Why didn't l think of this?

595
00:43:12,165 --> 00:43:14,041
Okay,
if l can recalculate,

596
00:43:14,209 --> 00:43:16,418
if l can account
for the difference in force,

597
00:43:16,586 --> 00:43:19,171
