00:43:50,829 --> 00:43:53,205
lt's becoming more
than our shielding can handle.

606
00:43:53,373 --> 00:43:55,916
Get the emergency generators
back online.

607
00:43:56,084 --> 00:43:59,545
The moment they stabilize,
