734
00:52:19,806 --> 00:52:22,558
Brooke: You don't understand.
This is a matter of life and death.

735
00:52:22,726 --> 00:52:25,936
- We can't leave without that radio.
- You're gonna leave without the radio

736
00:52:26,104 --> 00:52:28,981
because it's my radio.

737
00:52:29,149 --> 00:52:31,233
You know what l mean?

738
