739
00:52:38,575 --> 00:52:40,576
Hurry!
Go, go!

740
00:52:42,245 --> 00:52:43,787
Say your prayers,
you little bastard!

741
00:52:50,837 --> 00:52:52,671
How are we
supposed to get inside?

742
00:52:52,839 --> 00:52:54,840
There's no way
to sneak around that guard.

743
00:53:02,557 --> 00:53:05,726
- How'd you get that?
- l borrowed it.

744
00:53:06,978 --> 00:53:08,979
- Nice.
- Yeah.

